Crop Classifier¶

  • Classify plants in photo as corn, soyabean, or common weeds
  • Common weeds in ontario are wild carrot; Dandelion; Smooth groundcherry, Filed Horsetail, Tufted Vetch, and Other

Concerns¶

  • Multiple plants in each picture will make it difficult for the nueral net to get signals strong signals from one type.

In [5]:
def bing_image_search(key, term, max_images: int = 150, **kwargs):
    params = {'q':term, 'count':max_images}
    headers = {"Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key":key}
    search_url = "https://api.bing.microsoft.com/v7.0/images/search"
    response = requests.get(search_url,headers=headers, params=params)
    response.raise_for_status()
    search_results = response.json()
    return L(search_results['value'])

bing image search manually to asttempt to get better results. manual database tuning will be required corn - "corn sprouts" soyabean - "soyabean seedling" wild carrot - "wild carrot weed" dandelion - "dandelion type weeds seedlings" tufted vetch - "tufted vetch seedling" field horsetail - "field horsetail" smooth ground-cherry - "ground cherry seedling" spreading atriplex - "spreading atriplex" nodding beggarticks - "beggarticks weed" stink grass - "stink grass" tufted lovegrass - "tufted love grass" flixweed - "flixweed seedling" canada fleabane - "canada fleabane seedling" prickly lettuce - "prickly lettuce seedling" nipplewort - "nipplewort weed seedling" sow thistle - "sow thistle seedling"
